Lead Engineer
Lead Engineer
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  negotiableAmoria Bond is pleased to offer a unique opportunity within a well-reputed, multinational Oil & Gas company who require a Lead Engineer. This role will be primarily based in Singapore on a permanent basis.
The successful candidate will have a career background focused on Subsea Manifolds, Connections and Pipeline Systems. The successful candidate will have more than 8 years of experience and we would prefer candidates with Bachelors Degree or above in Science or Engineering.
We are looking for a true leader that can support and mentor a team of engineers whilst managing workload in a proactive and dynamic manner If you are motivated towards building up specialism within the Oil and Gas industry in a supportive and challenging environment that offers fantastic career progression by multiple avenues, this opportunity is definitely something to seriously take a look at.
Salaries will be dependent on skill set and experience but will be competitive.
If you are available immediately and would like further information on this role please forward your CV for immediate consideration to charlotte . chicv @ amoriabond . com
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business. No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
